</div></figure>



<p>Semelhante a empresas como a Apple, a <strong>Casper transformou algo tão mundano como retirar um produto de uma caixa em uma experiência memorável e compartilhável.</strong>&nbsp;</p>



<p>De fato, eles até te incentivam a documentar a sua experiência de unboxing em sua página de perguntas e respostas frequentes (FAQ).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="462" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png" alt="4 Casper_s FAQ Page" class="wp-image-113755" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-768x347.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-600x271.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-760x343.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1440x650.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-740x334.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-385x174.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page.png 1485w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>“Queremos vê-lo capturar a mágica! Documente o processo em um vídeo de unboxing e nos marque com o nome de usuário @casper.”</em></p>



<p>O unboxing, por si próprio, é outra moda capitalizada pela Casper, dado o seu crescente interesse nos anos recentes.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="442" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png" alt="5 Unboxing in Google Trends" class="wp-image-113759" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-300x129.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-768x331.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1536x662.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-380x164.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-600x259.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-760x328.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1440x621.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-740x319.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-385x166.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Os vídeos de unboxing da Casper são tão populares que possuem milhões de visualizações só no YouTube, resultando em publicidade gratuita para a empresa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png" alt="6 Casper Unboxing Video" class="wp-image-113763" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-2048x976.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1440x686.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-385x183.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Não é de surpreender que 53,86% de todo o tráfego social da Casper venha do YouTube (grande parte desse tráfego vem dos vídeos de seus <em>clientes</em> do que de seus próprios vídeos.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="259" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png" alt="7 Casper_s Social Traffic" class="wp-image-113767" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-300x76.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-768x194.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1536x388.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-380x96.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-600x152.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-760x192.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1440x364.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-139x35.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-198x50.png 198w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-740x187.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-220x56.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-385x97.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Quando você reinventa a experiência de compra, as pessoas prestam mais atenção.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Pergunte a si mesmo, “Será que eu posso reinventar a experiência de compra para meus clientes?” “Será que eu posso capitalizar numa tendência crescente para ajudar a entregar essa experiência?” “Será que eu posso tornar cada fase do ciclo de compra memorável e compartilhável?”</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>Estratégia nº2: Crie uma garantia imbatível</strong></h2>



<p>Imagine, por um momento, que você está em um pet shop e que seu filho está lhe implorando para comprar um cachorrinho.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Você não sabe se é uma boa ideia, então diz para ele, “não.”&nbsp;</p>



<p>O vendedor, ciente desta dinâmica, propõe o seguinte: “Vocês podem levar o cachorrinho para casa por um fim de semana. Se for muita responsabilidade, podem trazer de volta na segunda-feira e receber um reembolso completo, sem compromisso.”</p>



<p>Esperando secretamente que seu filho perca interesse até que o fim de semana acabe, você aceita levar o cachorrinho para casa. Com o passar do tempo, você descobre que estava certo. O seu filho <em>perdeu</em> interesse no cachorrinho—mas você acaba se apaixonando por ele. Chega a noite de domingo e você descobre que quer o cachorrinho mais do que o seu próprio filho. Ding. Ding.</p>



<p>O fechamento do cachorrinho (puppy-dog close), como é conhecido, é uma das técnicas de fechamento mais eficazes no livro do marketing. E, como é de se esperar, uma das técnicas que a Casper utiliza em seu marketing, notavelmente com sua garantia imbatível.</p>



<p>Para cada um de seus colchões, a Casper oferece um período de avaliação gratuita sem riscos de 100 noites.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="448" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png" alt="8 Casper_s Guarantee" class="wp-image-113771" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-768x336.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1536x672.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-600x263.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-760x333.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1440x630.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-114x50.png 114w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-740x324.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A promessa? Se você decidir que não gosta do colchão da Casper, eles mandam um transportador para retirá-lo de sua casa ou para doá-lo a uma caridade local ou para reciclá-lo. E o melhor de tudo, você nem precisa ter a caixa.</p>



<p>A Casper não está focada apenas em lucrar; ela também está interessada em ajudar outras pessoas que precisam e fazer sua parte pelo meio-ambiente. Isto é principalmente importante para a geração do milênio, que valoriza a caridade e o meio-ambiente como fatores decisivos principais para suas decisões de compra. (ht: Rikke.)</p>



<p>Há também um segundo benefício por oferecer uma avaliação gratuita de 100 noites. A Casper sabe que assim que o produto começa a fazer parte do dia-a-dia do cliente, mesmo se ele não gostar muito dele, ele terá bem menos vontade de devolvê-lo.</p>



<p>Como mencionado acima, a avaliação gratuita de 100 noites da Casper não é algo mencionado de forma casual e tardia (como em sua página de finalização de compra). Em vez disso, é algo consistente em todas as fases de seu funil (principalmente em seus e-mails de recuperação de carrinho, que discutiremos na 5ª parte: Estratégia nº1).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Você já deve estar oferecendo um tipo de garantia para seus produtos. Mas este tipo de garantia é imbatível? É algo que faz com que seus consumidores se apaixonem por você (e com que seus competidores te odeiem)? Caso não seja, considere abaixar a barreira de entrada para que sua oferta seja boa demais para seus clientes em potencial ignorarem.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>2ª parte: Marketing de conteúdo</strong></h2>



<p>A Casper utiliza três modelos de conteúdo como parte de sua estratégia, cada um com o objetivo de levar os clientes em potencial cada vez mais adiante no funil de compra.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para refrescar, aqui está um exemplo de um funil, incluindo exemplos dos modelos de conteúdo em casa fase:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="470" height="421" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel.png" alt="9 Purchase Funnel" class="wp-image-113775" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel.png 470w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-300x269.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-380x340.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-56x50.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-220x197.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-385x345.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px" /><figcaption>Fonte: <a href="http://cartina.se/guide-hur-jobba-med-content-marketing-har-ar-allt-du-behover-veta/tofu-mofu-bofu/">Cartina</a></figcaption></figure></div>



<p>Vamos dar uma olhada.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>Estratégia nº3: Responda às perguntas do seu público alvo (ToFu)</strong></h2>



<p>O blog da Casper, <a href="http://blog.casper.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pillow Talk</a>, é classificado como a primeira página com várias palavras-chave de comprimento médio, como “não consigo dormir” e “posições para dormir.” Ele também é classificado com pedidos de busca mais compridos e gerais como “o que fazer quando você não consegue dormir” e “como dormir mais cedo.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png" alt="10 Casper_s Organic Keywords" class="wp-image-113779" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-768x328.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-380x162.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-600x256.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-760x324.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-960x410.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-740x316.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-385x164.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Muito de seu conteúdo To-Fu é curto e humorístico, já outros, como veremos na 3ª parte: Estratégia nº2, são bem pesquisados.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="214" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png" alt="Casper Content Example" class="wp-image-113952" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-300x63.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-768x160.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1536x320.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-380x79.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-600x125.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-760x159.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1440x300.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-168x35.png 168w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-240x50.png 240w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-740x154.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-385x80.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Interessantemente, em vez de solicitar um endereço de e-mail nestas páginas, a Casper incentiva você a participar de uma pesquisa sobre seus hábitos de sono, oferecendo um desconto de $25 como recompensa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png" alt="11 Casper Survey Popup" class="wp-image-113783" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Em sua pesquisa, a Casper faz perguntas sobre suas posições para dormir favoritas, sua rotina noturna, além de questões demográficas gerais sobre sua idade, renda, gênero, entre outras:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png" alt="12 Preferred Sleeping Position" class="wp-image-113787" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>No fim da pesquisa, eles solicitam seu endereço de e-mail, antes de lhe oferecerem um código de desconto.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png" alt="13 Casper_s Survey Confirmation Page" class="wp-image-113791" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Casper até acompanha quantos visitantes clicam no link “Comprar na Casper” depois de completar a pesquisa para determinar se vale a pena continuar com a estratégia:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="27" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png" alt="14 Promo Code Labs" class="wp-image-113795" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-768x20.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1536x41.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-600x16.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-760x20.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1440x38.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-385x10.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E esta é uma sacada inteligente, por três motivos:</p>



<ol><li>Responder às perguntas mais pressionantes de seu público alvo aumenta o tráfego orgânico da Casper nas páginas de resultados dos motores de pesquisa (SERPs) e lhes posiciona como uma autoridade de mercado.</li><li>Fazer uma pesquisa com visitantes que vêm de pedidos de busca específicos lhes dá um grupo de foco altamente direcionado e feedback para que melhorem seu marketing.</li><li>Oferecer um desconto a um visitante que veio de uma busca orgânica impulsiona rapidamente os compradores sem a necessidade de pagar por tráfego (vamos falar mais a respeito disso na 4ª parte).&nbsp;</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Usando sites como o Quora e o Reddit, pesquise e descubra quais são as perguntas mais pressionantes do seu público alvo e crie um conteúdo que responde a essas perguntas. Para saber mais sobre como fazer isso, passo a passo, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">leia este artigo</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>Estratégia nº4: Crie um recurso de comparação acessível (MoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>Um obstáculo comum para comprar alguma coisa, como um colchão, é não saber se essa coisa serve para você.</p>



<p>Como mencionado acima, há várias considerações a serem feitas, como o tipo do colchão, o seu tamanho, a sua firmeza, entre outras.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>A Casper ajuda os compradores em potencial a superarem suas incertezas com o seu <a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/mattress-size-comparison-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">guia de comparação de tamanhos de colchões</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png" alt="15 Casper_s Mattress Comparison Guide" class="wp-image-113799" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Embora seja bem compridas, a Casper se classifica com centenas de palavras-chave na primeira posição, incluindo várias palavras-chave de comprimento longo, como “dimensões de cama tamanho king size” e “dimensões de colchão tamanho queen.”&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="374" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png" alt="16 Casper_s Positions in The SERPs" class="wp-image-113803" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-768x281.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-600x219.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-760x278.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-96x35.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-137x50.png 137w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-220x80.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E, para as palavras-chave que não classificam a Casper na primeira posição, ela se classifica como trecho em destaque (também conhecido como a posição nº 0).&nbsp;</p>



<p>Por exemplo, ao pesquisar “dimensões de cama tamanho queen size em pés,” a Casper se classifica em sexta posição (na data em que este artigo foi escrito), mas também se classifica como trecho em destaque, roubando <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/find-featured-snippets/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">8,6% de todos os cliques</a> como resultado.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="623" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png" alt="17 Queen Size Bed Dimensions in Feet" class="wp-image-113807" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-300x183.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-768x467.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-380x231.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-600x365.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-760x462.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-82x50.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-740x450.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-220x134.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-385x234.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>O que é interessante é que, em vez de solicitar seu feedback nesta página, como fazem em seu conteúdo To-Fu, a Casper lhe convida a entrar num sorteio. </p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5fd0b956f5f9b" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
