<p>Se você deslizar pela página, verá que eles também possuem um desconto para qualquer colchão da Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="274" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png" alt="27 Casper Discount Code 2" class="wp-image-113847" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-768x205.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1536x410.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-380x102.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-600x160.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-760x203.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1440x385.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-131x35.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-187x50.png 187w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-740x198.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-220x59.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-385x103.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Embora seja impossível saber se a Casper está ativamente entrando em contato com esses sites e outros, isso é bem provável, dada a frequência desses tipos de links—e dado o PageRank que eles trazem.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação: </strong>É fácil assumir que seja impossível construir links como esses acima. Mas vários sites, como o da CSUN, possuem um formulário onde você pode enviar seus próprios descontos. Pergunte a si mesmo, “Quem mais eu poderia servir?” Então, pense onde esse público alvo poderia estar e entre em contato com os sites certos.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="7"><strong>Estratégia nº7: Publique pesquisas originais (e se torne a autoridade principal em seu mercado)</strong></h2>



<p>Na Seção nº2, nós discutimos os três modelos de conteúdo que a Casper usa para gerar tráfego de busca. Você também aprendeu que um desses modelos se tratava de conteúdo que respondia às perguntas de seu público alvo.</p>



<p>A Casper faz um ótimo trabalho com isso. Mas, às vezes, responder a uma pergunta vai além de dar uma opinião. Na verdade, para se tornar uma autoridade em um assunto, você geralmente precisa fazer citações, ou até melhor, publicar uma pesquisa <em>original</em>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Considere, por exemplo, a publicação da Casper, “<a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/faqs/ca-the-mattress/how-often-should-i-replace-my-mattress/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Com que frequência eu devo substituir o meu colchão?</a>”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png" alt="28 How Often Should I Replace My Mattress" class="wp-image-113851" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nela, a Casper desmente um mito da indústria sobre o tempo de frequência que você deveria trocar o seu colchão.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Em vez de citar a pesquisa de outras pessoas, a Casper usa suas próprias descobertas, depois de terem pesquisado sobre seus próprios colchões, para esclarecer os fatos.</p>



<p>Esta página em seu FAQ possui um bom link DR90 da <a href="https://www.healthline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Healthline</a> que diz:&nbsp;</p>



<p><em>O conteúdo nem sempre tem que ser publicado em um blog para adquirir links.</em>&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Se você está criando conteúdo para seu site, considere publicar uma pesquisa original (até mesmo se for uma meta-análise de outros estudos) Sim, isso leva tempo. Mas isso também pode ser um recurso para que os sites em seu mercado referenciem com um link.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="8"><strong>Estratégia nº8: Use o “Gerador de backlinks melhor-de” (com uma diferença)</strong></h2>



<p>Uma das formas mais rápidas e fáceis dos varejistas online construírem seus links é serem destacados em conteúdo “o melhor-de”—conteúdo que lista os melhores dos melhores em nichos de mercado. (Eu chamo isso de “<a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">o gerador de backlinks melhor-de</a>”).</p>



<p>Por exemplo, a Casper construiu vários links em domínios de alta autoridade sendo destacada em conteúdo do tipo “melhores ideias para [palavra-chave]”, como por exemplo “melhores ideias para presentes de casamento.”</p>



<p>De fato, a Casper adquiriu vários links do-follow em vários sites de alta autoridade como <a href="https://www.theknot.com/content/top-40-registry-picks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Knot</a> (DR:90) e <a href="https://www.brides.com/story/wedding-registry-splurges-and-group-gifts" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Brides</a> (DR:82) utilizando esta mesma estratégia.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="230" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png" alt="29 Link from Brides" class="wp-image-113855" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-768x173.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1536x346.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-600x135.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-760x171.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1440x324.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-156x35.png 156w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-222x50.png 222w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-740x167.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-385x87.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Agora, é aqui que as coisas ficam interessantes.</p>



<p><a href="https://heavy.com/social/2016/03/top-best-bridal-shower-gift-ideas-gifts-wedding-bride-unique/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Heavy</a>, um site de notícias e informações, também destaca a Casper num artigo “melhor-de” chamado “melhores ideias para presentes de chá-de-panela.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png" alt="30 Top Bridal Shower Gift Ideas" class="wp-image-113859" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1536x749.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-600x293.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-760x371.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Mas ao vermos mais de perto, isto é na verdade um link de afiliado.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="25" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png" alt="31 Heavy Affiliate Link" class="wp-image-113863" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-300x7.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-768x19.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-380x9.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-600x15.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-760x19.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1440x35.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-180x4.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-250x6.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-740x18.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-220x5.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-385x9.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link.png 1475w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Embora seja muito improvável que um site como a Casper tenha entrado em contato para ter destaque num artigo assim, é muito provável que sites com o Heavy estejam interessados em inserir um link para um produto se houver uma chance de ganharem uma comissão por trás das cortinas. (Sendo assim, se você não possuir um programa de afiliados para seus produtos, considere que isso pode valer a pena.)</p>



<p>A melhor parte de ser destacado em um conteúdo “melhor-de” é que, obviamente, isso pode ser medido.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Utilizando uma ferramenta como o Ahrefs, você pode digitar o domínio de um competidor, clicar em “Domínios de referência &gt; Backlinks” para ver o tipo de conteúdo no qual está sendo destacado. Em seguida, você pode ir atrás de sites semelhantes. (Para saber mais sobre como fazer uma análise competitiva, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/competitive-analysis" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">leia este guia completo</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: O gerador de backlinks melhor-de é uma estratégia excelente se você vende produtos que são boas ideias para presentes. Usando alguns operadores de busca como “melhores presentes para [palavra-chave]” e “presentes de [palavra-chave] para [gênero],” identifique sites que poderiam incluir a sua oferta. Em seguida, entre em contato com eles. Sim, isso leva tempo. Mas é uma ótima estratégia para o link building de um comércio eletrônico.</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>4ª parte: Aquisição paga</strong></h2>



<p>Assim como várias empresas multimilionárias, a Casper investe uma fortuna em publicidade paga.</p>



<p>De fato, na data em que isto foi escrito, seu orçamento mensal estimado só para o Google Adwords é de $128.000. (Fonte: <a href="https://www.similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">SimilarWeb</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="398" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png" alt="32 Casper_s Paid Search" class="wp-image-113867" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-300x117.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-768x299.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1536x597.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-380x148.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-600x233.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-760x295.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1440x560.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-129x50.png 129w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-740x288.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-220x86.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-385x150.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Mas isso não quer dizer que suas estratégias não possam ser replicadas em menor escala.</p>



<p>Aqui estão minhas três estratégias favoritas que encontrei enquanto pesquisava.</p>



<h2 id="9"><strong>Strategy nº9: Traduza seus anúncios para capturar novos públicos</strong></h2>



<p>Um bom marqueteiro sabe quais países estão trazendo o maior tráfego ao seu site.</p>



<p>A Casper não é exceção.</p>



<p>Usando uma ferramenta como o <a href="http://similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">SimilarWeb</a>, podemos ver que a maioria do tráfego da Casper vem dos Estados Unidos, do Reino Unido, do Canadá, da França e da Alemanha.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="493" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png" alt="33 Casper_s Traffic by Countries" class="wp-image-113871" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-768x370.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1536x739.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-600x289.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-760x366.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1440x693.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Portanto, faz sentido que a Casper faz publicidade em inglês para os usuários dos Estados Unidos, do Reino Unido e do Canadá. Afinal de contas, nos Estados Unidos e no Reino Unido, (e em 56,9% do Canadá), o inglês é o idioma nativo.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas e quanto a países como a França e a Alemanha, onde o inglês não é o idioma principal?</p>



<p>A Casper está expandindo sua participação de mercado em outros países traduzindo seus anúncios para o idioma principal dos países alvos.</p>



<p>Considere, por exemplo, o seguinte anúncio de display, exibido para visitantes da Alemanha que visitaram anteriormente o site da Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="728" height="90" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png" alt="34 Casper_s German Display Ad" class="wp-image-113875" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png 728w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-300x37.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-380x47.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-600x74.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-250x31.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-385x48.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></figure></div>



<p>Quando clicado, os usuários são levados a uma página de destino com copywriting e suporte ao cliente em alemão.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png" alt="35 Casper_s German Landing Page" class="wp-image-113879" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Caso você tente sair, a Casper mostra um <a href="https://sleeknote.com/collect-email-addresses?ref=casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">pop-up de intenção de saída</a> solicitando seu endereço de e-mail.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="767" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png" alt="36 Casper_s German Exit Intent Popup" class="wp-image-113884" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-300x225.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-768x575.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-380x285.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-600x449.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-760x569.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1440x1079.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-654x490.png 654w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-220x165.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-385x288.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup.png 1455w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Em português, ele diz:</p>



<p>“Logo faremos com que um de seus sonhos se torne realidade. Inscreva-se e nunca ‘adormeça’ com as notícias, produtos e descontos da Casper.”</p>



<p>Esta estratégia funciona bem por três motivos:</p>



<ol><li>Traduzir um copy de anúncio para o idioma de um público alvo personaliza seu marketing.&nbsp;</li><li>Oferecer suporte ao cliente ajuda os leitores a superarem suas incertezas de compra (vamos falar mais a respeito disso na Estratégia nº12).</li><li>Capturar os endereços de e-mail dos visitantes que estão indo embora lhe dá uma oportunidade de fazer remarketing utilizando outro tipo de mídia (como e-mail).&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<p><strong>Ponto de ação:</strong> Entre no Google Analytics e clique em, “Público &gt; Visão geral &gt; País” para identificar seu público por país. Em seguida, traduza seu copy de anúncio para o idioma nativo de um ou mais desses países.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Nota do editor</strong></h3>



<p>Assista ao vídeo abaixo para saber como criar um pop-up de intenção de saída para uma página de destino específica utilizando o Sleeknote:</p>



<script src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/4scdrh0780.jsonp" async=""></script><script src="https://fast.wistia.com/assets/external/E-v1.js" async=""></script>
