<h2 id="10"><strong>Estratégia nº10: Experimente este truque pouco conhecido para monopolizar seus anúncios de pesquisa</strong></h2>



<p>Se você está utilizando os anúncios de pesquisa do Google para expandir seu negócio, você já sabe que você não pode ter mais do que um anúncio de pesquisa que leva os visitantes ao mesmo site simultaneamente.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas isso não impediu a Casper de monopolizar suas palavras-chave mais lucrativas.</p>



<p>Considere, por exemplo, “avaliações de colchões casper,” um pedido de busca que discutimos antes.</p>



<p>Isto é o que eu vejo quando pesquiso esse termo no Google. Percebe algo de interessante?</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="375" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png" alt="37 Casper_s Google Search Ads" class="wp-image-113888" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-768x282.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-600x220.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-760x279.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-95x35.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-136x50.png 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-220x81.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Casper domina três de quatro dos anúncios, direcionando os visitantes à Amazon, às avaliações do Google, e claro, ao seu próprio site. Todos esses sites são lojas online que vendem seus produtos. Além disso, a Casper possui um anúncio no Google Shopping à direita, fazendo com que seja quase impossível de ignorá-la.</p>



<p>Muito esperto, não acha?</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Esta estratégia é avançada, isso eu posso dizer. Mas se você conseguir concretizá-la, e seus produtos estiverem disponíveis em outros sites, considere enviar os visitantes a estes sites além do seu próprio.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="11"><strong>Estratégia nº11: Combine a publicidade com o remarketing para obter mais leads para sua loja online</strong></h2>



<p>Você já deve ter feito alguns experimentos com os Anúncios do Facebook.&nbsp;</p>



<p>E se tiver, é provável que você já tenha feito alguns experimentos com o remarketing usando a publicidade nativa.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas você já tentou fazer os dois ao mesmo tempo?</p>



<p>A Casper, sim. De fato, é algo que ela já está fazendo para conquistar novos clientes.</p>



<p>É assim que funciona.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Primeiro, a Casper faz publicidade de sua marca para novos públicos utilizando os Anúncios do Facebook.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="751" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png" alt="38 Casper Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-113892" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-768x563.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-380x279.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-600x440.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1440x1056.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-668x490.png 668w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad.png 1480w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nesses anúncios, ela convence os usuários a clicarem usando um gatilho mental de curiosidade (“O que é o fenômeno do unboxing e por que ele está dominando a Internet?”).</p>



<p>A partir desse ponto, a Casper leva os usuários a <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/casper-the-warby-parker-of-mattresses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">um artigo da CBS</a> que elogia o posicionamento de sua marca.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png" alt="39 How a Mattress Company Gains an Online Following" class="wp-image-113896" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Agora, você pode estar se perguntando, “De que adianta levar o tráfego a um site de terceiros sem nenhuma call-to-action (chamada para ação), além de desenvolver a prova social?”</p>



<p>Se você já pensou sobre isso, eu também fiquei pensando.</p>



<p>Até que eu deslizei até o fim da página…</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="503" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png" alt="40 Casper_s Native Ad" class="wp-image-113900" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-768x377.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1536x755.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-600x295.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-760x373.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1440x707.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-740x364.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Já que eu já tinha visitado seu site, particularmente a página de seu produto, a Casper me redirecionou utilizando um anúncio do <a href="https://www.criteo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Criteo</a>. De fato, eu sabia que isso não foi por acaso, porque o código de rastreamento estava visível no endereço URL:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="28" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png" alt="41 Casper Retargeting" class="wp-image-113904" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-768x21.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1536x42.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-600x17.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-760x21.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1440x40.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-385x11.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>I-na-cre-di-tá-vel.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Procure por um site que (a) elogie sua marca e (b) permita anúncios ou links patrocinados em seu site. Depois, faça um experimento levando tráfego do Facebook a esse site e acompanhe o número de referências através dos anúncios do site.</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>5ª parte: Email Marketing</strong></h2>



<p>Assim como várias outras lojas online, a Casper envia uma variedade de e-mails de marketing.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aqui, eu vou focar em três estratégias de e-mail específicas que ela está utilizando para levar seus clientes em potencial adiante em seu funil.</p>



<p>Vamos dar uma olhada.</p>



<h2 id="12"><strong>Estratégia nº12: Use este processo de abandono de carrinho de 3 passos para recuperar suas vendas perdidas</strong></h2>



<p>A Casper utiliza um processo de abandono de carrinho inteligente de 2 passos para recuperar os compradores indecisos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Quando eu abandonei meu carrinho, eu recebi o primeiro de dois e-mails de recuperação de carrinho um dia depois.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png" alt="42 Casper_s Cart Recovery Email" class="wp-image-113908" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-768x346.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Neste e-mail, a Casper me convidou a concretizar minha compra. Nada de estranho nisso. Mas abaixo da call-to-action, havia um GIF, destacando as perguntas mais frequentes, e um convite para entrar em contato caso eu tivesse alguma dúvida.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif" alt="43 Casper_s Cart Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-113912" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-300x169.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-768x432.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1536x864.gif 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-380x214.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-600x338.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-760x428.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1440x810.gif 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-62x35.gif 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-89x50.gif 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-740x416.gif 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-220x124.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-385x217.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Convidar os visitantes que estão indo embora a entrarem em contato não é apenas um exemplo de um ótimo serviço ao cliente, como também é uma ótima forma de superar as incertezas potenciais que não foram resolvidas durante a primeira visita de um cliente em potencial. Além disso, a Casper oferece várias formas de entrar em contato, fazendo com que você tenha suas dúvidas respondidas da forma mais fácil possível para concretizar a sua compra.</p>



<p>Eu resolvi não retornar ao meu carrinho. Então, um dia seguinte, eu recebi um segundo e-mail.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="788" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png" alt="44 Casper Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-113916" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png 788w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-231x300.png 231w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-768x998.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-1182x1536.png 1182w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-380x494.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-600x780.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-760x988.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-377x490.png 377w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-220x286.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-385x501.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 788px) 100vw, 788px" /></figure></div>



<p>Neste e-mail, a Casper enfatiza a garantia imbatível que vimos na Estratégia nº1, fazendo com que o processo para que eu concretize a minha compra seja o mais fácil possível.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="299" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png" alt="45 Casper Guarantee" class="wp-image-113920" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-300x88.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-768x224.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-380x111.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-600x175.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-760x222.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-120x35.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-171x50.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-740x216.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-220x64.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-385x112.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>O mais interessante a respeito da Casper é sua capacidade de reconhecer suas vantagens injustas—como sua avaliação gratuita de 100 noites—e usá-las em cada fase de seu marketing. E é aí que se encontra uma lição importante:</p>



<p>Você pode não ser capaz de competir com seu competidor quando se trata de oferecer frete grátis, garantias de 3 meses e outras expectativas que os consumidores têm. Porém, você pode usar o que diferencia o seu negócio e lembrar os clientes em potencial regularmente disso.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Se você tem uma loja online e envia e-mails de recuperação de carrinho, dê aos compradores em potencial uma oportunidade de entrarem em contato com você. Em seguida, ajude-os a superar quaisquer incertezas que tenham para que concretizem a sua compra.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="13"><strong>Estratégia nº13: Transforme os consumidores em vendedores com este sistema de referências replicável</strong></h2>



<p>Se você leu minha publicação sobre o <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Marketing de Harry’s</a>, você já deve saber que a Harry’s recebeu 100.000 endereços de e-mail em apenas sete dias—antes mesmo de fazer sequer uma única venda.</p>



<p>A Casper desenvolveu um sistema de referências semelhante para seu marketing pós-compra, convidando os clientes a indicarem a marca aos seus amigos.</p>



<p>É assim que funciona.</p>



<p>Após efetuar uma compra na Casper, você recebe um e-mail de confirmação de compra. Nada de estranho nisso. Mas é aqui que as coisas ficam interessantes…</p>



<p>No rodapé do e-mail, há um link de referência que você pode enviar para seus amigos e ganhar prêmios.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="538" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png" alt="46 Casper_s Referral Program in Email Footer" class="wp-image-113924" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-300x158.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-768x403.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-380x200.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-600x315.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-760x399.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-740x389.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-220x116.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption>Fonte: <a href="https://reallygoodemails.com/wp-content/uploads/thank-you-for-your-order-r650000650.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Really Good Emails</a></figcaption></figure></div>



<p>Isto cria um <em>gatilho mental de curiosidade</em>. Os prêmios não são especificados, então você é motivado a clicar para saber mais.</p>



<p>Quando você clica em “Saber mais,” você é redirecionado a uma página no site da Casper onde você recebe um vale-presente da Amazon a cada pessoa indicada.&nbsp;</p>



<p>E o melhor de tudo?</p>



<p>A Casper faz com que o compartilhamento seja super simples, dependendo do seu tipo preferido de mídia.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png" alt="47 Casper Referral Code" class="wp-image-113928" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1536x746.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Por exemplo, se você clicar em “E-mail,” a Casper ativa um e-mail pronto para que você não tenha que escrever a mensagem por conta própria.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="710" height="610" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png" alt="48 Casper_s Prewritten Email" class="wp-image-113932" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png 710w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-300x258.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-380x326.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-600x515.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-570x490.png 570w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-220x189.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-385x331.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px" /></figure></div>



<p>Isso economiza seu tempo e é uma ótima forma de simplificar o processo de deixar uma avaliação.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Seus clientes são os melhores vendedores que existem. Portanto, convide-os para que eles fiquem incentivados a indicarem a sua marca. Você pode não ser capaz de oferecer vales-presente da Amazon (poucos são capazes de oferecer), mas você pode oferecer <em>outra coisa</em> (por exemplo, um desconto para uma compra futura).</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="14"><strong>Estratégia nº14: Receba melhores avaliações de clientes com este truque de copywriting simples, mas poderoso</strong></h2>



<p>Como mencionado acima, a Casper utiliza e-mails de confirmação para convencer os novos compradores a indicarem amigos.</p>



<p>Mas essa nem sempre foi sua estratégia…</p>



<p>No início, enquanto desenvolvia sua autoridade no mercado, a Casper criou sua reputação através das <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">avaliações</a>.</p>



<p>Era assim que funcionava:</p>



<p>Alguns dias depois de se tornar um novo cliente, a Casper lhe convidava a deixar uma avaliação em seu site.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png" alt="49 Casper_s Review Email" class="wp-image-113936" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-300x251.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-768x643.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-380x318.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-600x503.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-760x637.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-585x490.png 585w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-220x184.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-385x322.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Depois de clicar no call-to-action, você era redirecionado à página de avaliações da Casper. Nela, a Casper lhe orientava a enviar seus comentários usando várias perguntas como exemplo.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="749" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png" alt="50 Casper_s Review Submission Form" class="wp-image-113940" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-300x219.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-768x562.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1536x1123.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-600x439.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-760x556.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1440x1053.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-670x490.png 670w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>“Você gostou da experiência de unboxing? Como foi dormir no colchão da Casper comparado com sua cama antiga? Você indicaria a Casper a um amigo?”</em></p>



<p>A Casper sabe que os consumidores tendem a escrever avaliações genéricas quando solicitados, então, naquela época, ela orientava os consumidores a escreverem sobre as áreas que eram importantes para ela (a Casper). Isso incluía a experiência de unboxing e se os consumidores indicariam a Casper para um amigo.</p>



<p>E isso funcionou.</p>



<p>A Casper recebeu centenas de avaliações que responderam a tudo acima.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="247" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1024x247.png" alt="51 Casper Review" class="wp-image-113944" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1024x247.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-768x185.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1536x370.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-380x92.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-600x145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-760x183.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1440x347.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-207x50.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-740x178.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review.png 1680w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Hoje, a Casper reaproveita estas avaliações no seu marketing, particularmente nos e-mails de onboarding. Aqui está o quarto e-mail que você recebe depois de se inscrever para receber atualizações da Casper:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="598" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-1024x598.png" alt="52 Review in Email" class="wp-image-113948" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-1024x598.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-768x449.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-380x222.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-600x351.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-760x444.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-740x432.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-220x129.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-385x225.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email.png 1198w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>“AVALIAÇÕES DESTACADAS</em></p>



<p><em>Conforto excelente</em></p>



<p><em>Processo simples para compra, entrega, desempacotamento e instalação. Ótimo serviço ao cliente para qualquer problema. Sono maravilhoso durante o último mês e espero ter vários anos de aproveitamento. Até os cachorros perceberam como o Colchão da Casper é ótimo. Contei a todos os meus amigos sobre como é maravilhoso dormir na cama, sobre como o processo é super fácil e sobre a garantia incrível. Continuem com o ótimo trabalho, pessoal!! Mencionem nossos nomes e nós dois podemos ganhar dinheiro com isso!!!!”</em></p>



<p>Nenhuma quantidade de copywriting que você escrever pode superar o elogio de um cliente. Portanto, use suas melhores avaliações em seus e-mails. E use regularmente.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Convide os novos clientes a avaliarem sua compra após algum tempo. Em seguida, oriente-os a escrever sobre as coisas certas, com base nas incertezas em potencial sobre a compra do seu produto ou nas áreas que você deseja destacar. Por fim, reaproveite estas avaliações em seu marketing.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fc4f131f6165" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Baixe o kit de ferramentas do Marketing de Casper  </h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p>Este artigo levou 20 horas para escrever. Vinte. Não preciso nem dizer que houve MUITA coisa que eu não pude incluir nesta publicação. Para deixar nossa vida mais fácil, eu compilei um swipe file com os materiais do marketing da Casper. Além disso, algumas coisinhas extras (*coff* uma estratégia bônus que é boa demais e não deve ser ignorada).</p>
<p>Tenha acesso ao kit de ferramentas do Marketing de Casper e gere mais tráfego e um maior engajamento hoje (inclui conteúdo bônus não presente na publicação, exemplos de e-mail, anúncios do Facebook, entre outros).</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Baixe Nosso Recurso Agora Mesmo →">Baixe Nosso Recurso Agora Mesmo →</a>
            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Baixe o kit de ferramentas do Marketing de Casper  ">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>Conclusão</strong></h2>



<p>Pronto, aí está: as melhores estratégias do marketing da Casper em menos de 6.000 palavras.</p>



<p>Vamos avaliar cada uma mais uma vez:</p>



<ol><li>Estratégia nº1: Reinvente a experiência de compra</li><li>Estratégia nº2: Crie uma garantia imbatível</li><li>Estratégia nº3: Responda às perguntas do seu público alvo (ToFu)</li><li>Estratégia nº4: Crie um recurso de comparação acessível (MoFu)</li><li>Estratégia nº5: Mostre todas as avaliações em um só lugar (BoFu)</li><li>Estratégia nº6: Crie links .edu white-hat com o “Método CSD”</li><li>Estratégia nº7: Publique pesquisas originais (e se torne a autoridade principal em seu mercado)</li><li>Estratégia nº8: Use o “Gerador de backlinks melhor-de” (com uma diferença)</li><li>Estratégia nº9: Traduza seus anúncios para capturar novos públicos</li><li>Estratégia nº10: Experimente este truque pouco conhecido para monopolizar seus anúncios de pesquisa</li><li>Estratégia nº11: Combine a publicidade com o remarketing para obter mais leads para sua loja online</li><li>Estratégia nº12: Use este processo de abandono de carrinho de 3 passos para recuperar suas vendas perdidas</li><li>Estratégia nº13: Transforme os consumidores em vendedores com este sistema de referências replicável</li><li>Estratégia nº14: Receba melhores avaliações de clientes com este truque de copywriting simples, mas poderoso</li></ol>



<p>Meu conselho? Escolha uma das estratégias acima, depois invista tempo para a implementá-la, e em seguida, melhore-a ainda mais.</p>



<p>Agora, eu quero lhe fazer uma pergunta:</p>



<p><strong>Quais das estratégias do marketing de Casper você experimentará primeiro?</strong></p>



<p><em>Você experimentará o “Método CSD”? Ou irá traduzir os seus anúncios para capturar novos públicos? Deixe um comentário abaixo.</em></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/marketing-de-casper">Marketing de Casper: Como uma empresa de colchões foi do zero a $750 milhões em 4 anos (caso de estudo)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt">Sleeknote</a>.</p>
