<h2 id="1">1. Entendendo o Público da Empresa BarkBox</h2>



<p>Apresentamos a <em>BarkBox</em> em nosso <em>blog</em> várias vezes ao longo dos anos (ou seja, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">aqui</a> e <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">aqui</a>). Depois de navegar em seu <em>site</em> por alguns minutos, não é difícil de entender o por quê. Utilizando essas imagens fofas de cachorrinhos e palavras assertivas e carinhosas, é preciso dizer mais?</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="462" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-1024x462.png" alt="1 BarkBox Copywriting Example" class="wp-image-110880" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-1024x462.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-768x347.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-1536x693.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-600x271.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-760x343.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-1440x650.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-740x334.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example-385x174.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-BarkBox-Copywriting-Example.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Brincadeiras à parte, a empresa<em> </em>se solidificou e atinge seu público inteiramente. Desde o uso da linguagem do comprador-alvo, dando atenção também a importância dos cuidados com os animais, até a venda direta para esses donos de cães, a <em>BarkBox</em> é uma marca que frequentemente é imitada, mas raramente duplicada.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="336" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-1024x336.png" alt="2 BarkBox 2 Copywriting Example" class="wp-image-110884" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-1024x336.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-300x98.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-768x252.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-1536x504.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-380x125.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-600x197.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-760x249.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-1440x473.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-107x35.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-152x50.png 152w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-740x243.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-220x72.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example-385x126.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-BarkBox-2-Copywriting-Example.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>Observe como, na Etapa 2, BarkBox vende, não para o próprio comprador, mas para o animal de estimação do comprador. Os cães não podem verbalizar sua insatisfação (ou qualquer coisa nesse sentido, infelizmente), assim é uma jogada de marketing inteligente da empresa.</em></p>



<p>Não importa que negócio você esteja envolvido, se está vendendo brinquedos baratos para cães ou algo mais sofisticado, as pessoas querem se sentir compreendidas pelas marcas em que investem seu tempo e dinheiro. Isso pode ser o que elas pensam de si mesmas ou das pessoas que aspiram se tornar.</p>



<p>Se você demonstrar isso, tanto em seus textos de <em>Copywriting</em> quanto em outros materiais de <em>marketing</em>, e articular os objetivos, desejos, esperanças e medos dos seus clientes potenciais, seus produtos sairão das prateleiras digitais mais rápido do que você pode reabastecê-los.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
