<h2><strong>Use estes 7 exemplos de depoimentos para obter mais clientes</strong></h2>



<ol><li><a href="#1">Depoimento Citado</a></li><li><a href="#2">Depoimento de Influencer</a></li><li><a href="#3">Depoimento de Redes Sociais</a></li><li><a href="#4">Opinião de Clientes</a></li><li><a href="#5">Estudos de Caso</a></li><li><a href="#6">Depoimento em Vídeo</a></li><li><a href="#7">Série de Documentário</a></li></ol>





<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Depoimento Citado</strong></h2>



<p>Existem três tipos de depoimento citado.&nbsp;</p>



<ol><li>Citado;</li><li>Citado com imagem de herói; e</li><li>Citado com imagem de herói e call-to-action (CTA)</li></ol>



<p>Vamos discutir rapidamente sobre cada um deles.&nbsp;</p>





<h3><strong>i. Citado&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Todos nós estamos familiarizados com eles. E se você for sortudo o suficiente, pode ser que você tenha tido a oportunidade de ter um desses na sua foto escolar:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="510" height="386" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture.png" alt="Home Simpson Yearbook Picture" class="wp-image-90465" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture.png 510w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-300x227.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-380x288.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-66x50.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-220x167.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-385x291.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px" /></figure></div>



<p>A citação é um dos primeiros tipos de depoimentos (e um dos mais fáceis de se conseguir). Surgindo primeiramente nos jornais, atualmente as citações são comuns em páginas de produtos. Elas têm o propósito de inspirar nos visitantes a confiança de que a compra que eles estão pensando em fazer é uma boa decisão.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.poopourri.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Poo~Pourri</a> usa uma barra deslizante em sua página inicial para apresentar seus depoimentos:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="505" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1024x505.png" alt="Poo~Pourri Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90505" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1024x505.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1536x757.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1440x710.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Acrescentar recursos adicionais como uma barra deslizante—ou no caso do Poo~Pourri, uma barra deslizante com uma avaliação de “estrelas”— dá aos leitores mais motivos para estabelecer uma relação e legitima ainda mais os depoimentos.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>





<h3><strong>ii. Citado com imagem de herói</strong></h3>



<p>As citações, embora sejam fáceis de conseguir, também são fáceis de se produzir. As empresas sabem disso. E é exatamente por isso que muitas adicionam imagens de heróis em seus depoimentos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Fotos legitimam ainda mais um depoimento e, em muitos casos, aumentam muito as conversões.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Na verdade, quando a <a href="http://www.160drivingacademy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">160 Driving Academy</a> substituiu seu banco de imagens de heróis por fotos de pessoas reais, eles<a href="https://vwo.com/success-stories/160-driving-academy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"> aumentaram sua taxa de conversão em 161%</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="566" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-1024x566.png" alt="161 Driving Academy Split Test" class="wp-image-90409" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-1024x566.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.shopify.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Shopify</a> apresenta imagens de heróis em alta-resolução para acompanhar seus depoimentos. Quando você vê uma citação de um consumidor—assim como você—é mais fácil criar empatia e avançar para realizar uma compra:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="387" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1024x387.png" alt="Shopify Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90513" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1024x387.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-300x113.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-768x290.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1536x580.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-380x143.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-600x227.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-760x287.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1440x544.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-93x35.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-132x50.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-740x279.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-220x83.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-385x145.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Se clientes evangélicos falam sobre você de forma alegre e empolgada, por que não mostrá-los de uma forma legal, também?</p>





<h3><strong>iii. Citado com imagem de herói e call-to-action (CTA)</strong></h3>



<p>Você acha que uma citação e uma imagem de herói são suficientes para que um possível cliente compre algo, certo? Errado.</p>



<p>Como publicitários, nós nunca podemos imaginar que os potenciais clientes sabem o que fazer; temos que pegá-los pela mão e mostrar a eles. E é exatamente por isso que os bons depoimentos sempre precisam de uma boa chamada para ação, ou <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> (CTA).</p>



<p>Seguindo o exemplo do Shopify, <a href="https://maruccisports.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Marucci</a> apresenta uma citação com uma imagem de herói e uma CTA, convidando os leitores a ler um estudo de caso:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1024x475.png" alt="Marucci Customer Testimonials" class="wp-image-90477" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1024x475.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-768x356.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1536x712.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1440x668.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-740x343.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Se o visitante estiver interessado, ele pode saber mais sobre a transformação de David Ortiz antes de decidir se Marucci é a melhor opção.</p>



<p><a href="https://zapier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Zapier</a> vai além em relação aos depoimentos. E este é um ótimo exemplo do que é dar um passo a mais. Em vez de apresentar seus depoimentos em uma página específica, eles incluem os depoimentos em <em>posts</em> relevantes, especialmente na forma caixas deslizantes:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="348" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-1024x348.png" alt="Zapier Slide-In Testimonial" class="wp-image-90533" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-1024x348.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-300x102.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-768x261.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-380x129.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-600x204.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-760x258.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-147x50.png 147w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-740x251.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-385x131.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Nota do editor</strong></h3>



<p>Esta é uma forma rápida e fácil de mostrar os depoimentos certos nas páginas certas usando Sleeknote:</p>



<script src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/nrunfq9k0r.jsonp" async=""></script><script src="https://fast.wistia.com/assets/external/E-v1.js" async=""></script><div class="wistia_responsive_padding" style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><div class="wistia_responsive_wrapper" style="height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%;"><div class="wistia_embed wistia_async_nrunfq9k0r videoFoam=true" style="height:100%;position:relative;width:100%"><div class="wistia_swatch" style="height:100%;left:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;position:absolute;top:0;transition:opacity 200ms;width:100%;"><img src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/nrunfq9k0r/swatch" style="filter:blur(5px);height:100%;object-fit:contain;width:100%;" alt="" aria-hidden="true" onload="this.parentNode.style.opacity=1;"></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>





<p>Uma maneira de se diferenciar ao escrever depoimentos é usando o que o Copyblogger chama de <a href="http://www.copyblogger.com/testimonials-part-1/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>depoimento reverso</em></a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>É quando um depoimento inicia com uma objeção por parte do comprador, para depois continuar com o elogio e encerrar superando o ceticismo inicial.</p>



<p>Aqui está um exemplo do <a href="http://bonytobeastly.com/transformations/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bony to Beastly</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="729" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-1024x729.png" alt="Bony to Beastly Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90425" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-1024x729.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-768x547.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-600x427.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-760x541.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-688x490.png 688w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-385x274.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial.png 1110w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Neste exemplo, Dallas aborda uma preocupação comum que os clientes têm quando compram online (“Isso é um golpe?”) para depois migrar para a transformação que ele sofreu ao tomar uma atitude (ou, em outras palavras, fazer uma compra).</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Se você está usando um depoimento de citação, certifique-se de que todos possuam uma imagem de herói e uma CTA relevante que dê aos visitantes a oportunidade de saber mais sobre a transformação do cliente, em vez do produto.</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Depoimento de influencer</strong></h2>



<p>Os influenciadores são muito parecidos com os jogadores de futebol da escola. São muito populares entre os colegas, mas é quase impossível ser amigo de um.</p>



<p>Ganhar aquele cobiçado cumprimento de um influencer no hall de entrada é algo incrível. Mas o que é realmente incrível—e onde você deveria focar seus esforços—é conseguir a publicidade de influenciadores no <em>seu </em>negócio.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pense nisso: todo mundo quer aparecer na Entrepreneur, Forbes, The Huffington Post, etc. Mas tem um problema.</p>



<p><em>Todos estão correndo atrás disso. </em>O melhor é ser notado por alguma pessoa conhecida, com a qual o seu público está mais familiarizado.</p>



<p>Vamos pegar <a href="http://www.dibruno.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Di Bruno Bros.</a> como exemplo. Eles são especializados em encontrar os mais deliciosos queijos, carnes e especialidades gastronômicas por aí. E seu esforço vale a pena.</p>



<p>Por ter atraído a atenção de gigantes do mercado como <em>Travel + Leisure</em> e <em>Serious Eats </em>(entre outros), Di Bruno Bros combina citações e marcas de influencers em sua página de mídia:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1024x491.png" alt="Di Bruno Bros. Media Testimonials" class="wp-image-90457" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1536x737.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-760x365.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1440x691.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials.png 1720w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Você nem sempre conseguirá atrair influencers, isso é fato. Mas você sempre pode aumentar suas chances de ser notado sendo o melhor naquilo que você faz.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Entre em contato com autoridades da sua indústria e pergunte se eles gostariam de experimentar seu produto.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Depoimento de redes sociais</strong></h2>



<p>As redes sociais têm mudado a forma como nos expressamos. Quando não estamos postando nosso almoço no Instagram ou pedindo likes, estamos indo para as redes sociais para dar voz aos nossos sonhos, medos e, eventualmente, frustrações com nossas marcas favoritas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="635" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-1024x635.png" alt="Royal Mail Funny Tweet" class="wp-image-90509" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-1024x635.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-768x477.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-760x472.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet.png 1270w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Quando é positivo, todos elogiam. E isso é legítimo. A vantagem em relação ao depoimento citado, é que o depoimento social é eficaz porque é possível clicar e ver se a pessoa cuja opinião você está lendo é uma pessoa <em>real</em>, vivendo uma vida <em>real</em>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Casper</a> inclui tweets e postagens do Instagram dos clientes em seu site para destacar o quão confortáveis são seus produtos:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="434" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1024x434.png" alt="Capser Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90429" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1024x434.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-300x127.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-768x326.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1536x651.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-380x161.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-600x254.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-760x322.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1440x611.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-118x50.png 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-740x314.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-385x163.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial.png 1580w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Fabletics incentiva seus clientes a compartilhar imagens próprias usando o produto no Instagram com a hashtag #MyFabletics&#8230;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="473" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1024x473.png" alt="My Fabletics Instagram Posts" class="wp-image-90489" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1024x473.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-768x355.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1536x710.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-600x277.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-760x351.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1440x665.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts.png 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;e é exatamente isso que eles fazem.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="518" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1024x518.png" alt="My Fabletics Top Posts" class="wp-image-90493" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1024x518.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-300x152.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-768x388.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1536x777.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-380x192.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-600x303.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-760x384.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1440x728.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-99x50.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-740x374.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-220x111.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-385x195.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts.png 1720w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Até agora, a hashtag #MyFabletics já foi usada <em>mais de 37,000 vezes:</em></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="382" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-1024x382.png" alt="My Fabletics Hashtag" class="wp-image-90485" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-1024x382.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-768x286.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-600x224.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-760x283.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-94x35.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-134x50.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-740x276.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag.png 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Convide seus clientes para deixar um feedback nas redes sociais depois de fazer uma compra. Então, inclua qualquer feedback positivo nas páginas do seu produto.</p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Opinião de clientes&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Provavelmente você está familiarizado com a prova social, <em>que é a nossa tendência a assumir que as ações dos outros refletem o comportamento correto numa determinada situação.</em></p>



<p>Mas nem todas as formas de influência são iguais. O mais importante é quando as ações dos outros pertencem a pessoas <em>parecidas</em> conosco.</p>



<p><a href="http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article/file?type=supplementary&amp;id=info:doi/10.1371/journal.pone.0106606.s001" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Em uma pesquisa de 2008</a>, os hóspedes de um hotel, quando lhes foi dito que a maioria dos hóspedes anteriores que ocuparam <em>seu quarto específico</em> se mostraram mais dispostos a reutilizar suas toalhas do que aqueles que ouviram as normas gerais do hotel.</p>



<p>Colocando de outra maneira, <em>nós preferimos pessoas que pensam como nós</em>. Se você se assemelha a um comprador anterior, você tende a ser mais receptivo em relação ao seu depoimento. Por isso, não é uma surpresa sermos tão sensíveis às opiniões dos clientes.</p>



<p>Na verdade, <a href="https://www2.deloitte.com/content/dam/Deloitte/uk/Documents/consumer-business/consumer-review-8-the-growing-power-of-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">de acordo com a pesquisa feita pela Deloitte</a>, 60 por cento das pessoas consideram as opiniões <em>tão confiáveis quanto</em> as informações de seus amigos e familiares.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="592" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-1024x592.png" alt="Most Trusted Source of Information on Products and Services" class="wp-image-90481" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-1024x592.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-768x444.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-380x220.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-600x347.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-760x440.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-740x428.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-385x223.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Marcas como <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank">Harry’s</a>, uma empresa de produtos para barbear, usa o <a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">TrustPilot</a> para aumentar sua confiabilidade.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="453" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1024x453.png" alt="Harry_s Trustpilot Reviews" class="wp-image-90461" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1024x453.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-768x340.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1536x680.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-380x168.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-600x266.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-760x336.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1440x638.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-113x50.png 113w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-740x328.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-220x97.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-385x170.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As opiniões de clientes normalmente são os depoimentos mais fáceis entre os sete tipos abordados porque é muito fácil solicitá-las. De fato, <a href="http://reallygoodemails.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">a Casper envia um e-mail após a compra</a>, pedindo que os clientes escrevam uma opinião:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="790" height="670" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email.png" alt="Casper Review Email" class="wp-image-90437" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email.png 790w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-300x254.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-768x651.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-380x322.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-600x509.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-760x645.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-59x50.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-578x490.png 578w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-220x187.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-385x327.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Envie um e-mail para seus clientes 14 dias após a compra pedindo que deixem uma opinião em um site de opiniões relevantes para o mercado. Então, mostre as opiniões em seu site.</p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Estudos de Caso</strong></h2>



<p>Os estudos de caso são uma oportunidade para <em>realmente </em>vender ao leitor com base na transformação que um cliente anterior teve.</p>



<p>Usando uma <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">fórmula de copywriting</a> como a <em>Before-After-Bridge</em> (BAB), você pode mostrar aos leitores onde os clientes estavam <em>antes</em> de fazer a compra, onde eles estão agora, <em>depois</em> de fazer a compra, e fazer a ligação usando o seu produto ou serviço.</p>



<p><a href="https://blog.bufferapp.com/copywriting-formulas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Kevan Lee do Buffer</a> resume a fórmula BAB de forma incrível:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="356" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1024x356.png" alt="Before After Bridge Formula" class="wp-image-90417" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1024x356.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-300x104.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-768x267.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1536x534.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-380x132.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-600x209.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-760x264.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1440x501.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-101x35.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-144x50.png 144w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-740x257.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-385x134.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula.png 1755w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Steve Kamb do <a href="https://www.nerdfitness.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>Nerd Fitness</em></a> usa um estudo de caso como uma maneira de <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank">gerar leads</a> para o seu produto principal, The NerdFitness Academy. Kamb apresenta de forma inteligente os <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank">e-mails dos clientes</a> para apoiar suas histórias, legitimando o estudo de caso no processo:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="814" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-1024x814.png" alt="Nerd Fitness Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90497" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-1024x814.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-300x238.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-768x611.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-380x302.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-600x477.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-760x604.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-63x50.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-616x490.png 616w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-220x175.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-385x306.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial.png 1190w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Convide um cliente para contar sua história particular após ter usado seu produto, e foque na transformação pela qual ele passou ao fazer isso.</p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Depoimento em vídeo&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Os vídeos estão rapidamente se tornando o principal canal publicitário para os donos de empresas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Na verdade, <a href="https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Which-Content-Marketing-Tactics-Best-ROI/1009706" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">de acordo com um relatório da Copypress</a>, 51,9% dos profissionais da publicidade no mundo todo consideram o vídeo como o tipo de conteúdo com o melhor RDI.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="860" height="745" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI.png" alt="Content with Best ROI" class="wp-image-90441" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI.png 860w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-300x260.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-768x665.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-380x329.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-600x520.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-760x658.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-40x35.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-566x490.png 566w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-220x191.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-385x334.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px" /></figure></div>



<p>Marcas como Harry’s e Orabrush aparentemente se tornaram virais do dia para a noite ao potencializar o poder do vídeo para divulgar seus serviços. <a href="https://www.quicksprout.com/2013/11/27/if-a-picture-says-1000-words-than-video-is-priceless/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Como Neil Patel diz</a>, <em>“Se uma imagem vale por mil palavras, então um vídeo é incalculável.”</em></p>



<p>Mas o vídeo não se limita ao marketing de um produto. Ramit Sethi do <a href="http://www.iwillteachyoutoberich.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>I Will Teach You to Be Rich</em></a><em> </em>usa o vídeo para divulgar seu produto principal, Zero to Launch—porém, com um toque a mais. Em vez de focar no benefício para quem está assistindo, Ramit se diferencia ao focar na transformação de clientes <em>anteriores</em>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Combinando valores de uma produção profissional com entrevistas esclarecedoras e acompanhando estudos de caso, Ramit usa seus alunos mais bem-sucedidos como vitrine para vender seu curso. (Observe a chamada “Quick Wins de Sucesso” acima do vídeo para os leitores rápidos):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="505" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1024x505.png" alt="Maria B. Success Story" class="wp-image-90473" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1024x505.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1536x757.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1440x710.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Outros empreendedores, como Orabrush, já citado, apresentam os depoimentos de vídeo dos clientes em sua página inicial:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="340" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-1024x340.png" alt="Orabrush Customer Testimonials" class="wp-image-90501" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-1024x340.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-300x100.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-768x255.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-380x126.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-600x199.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-760x252.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-106x35.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-151x50.png 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-740x245.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-220x73.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-385x128.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Um tempo atrás, os depoimentos em vídeo eram reservados para as empresas com um orçamento de publicidade de 6 dígitos. Mas atualmente qualquer um com um smartphone pode gravar um vídeo em qualquer lugar, a qualquer momento, e registrar seus pensamentos sobre suas marcas favoritas.&nbsp;</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Peça aos clientes para gravarem um vídeo de depoimento curto com seus smartphones, falando sobre o que eles mais gostaram sobre a sua marca. Então, apresente os vídeos aos potenciais clientes em momentos específicos na sua jornada de compra.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Série de documentário</strong></h2>



<p>Assim como a maioria dos publicitários, eu pensei que já tinha visto tudo em relação ao depoimento de clientes. Até que eu conheci Bryan Harris.</p>



<p>Em 2016, Bryan lançou o seu produto principal, Get 10,000 Subscribers, mas foi além e entrevistou seus clientes anteriores: <em>Ele filmou uma série de documentário.</em></p>



<p>Com uma equipe de filmagem na mão, Bryan visitou três ex-alunos em suas casas para documentar como suas vidas tinham mudado após participar do seu curso.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="580" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-1024x580.png" alt="Underrated" class="wp-image-90525" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-1024x580.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-300x170.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-768x435.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-380x215.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-600x340.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-760x431.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-740x419.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-220x125.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-385x218.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E os resultados foram incríveis.</p>



<p>Os espectadores amaram, os clientes em potencial compraram o produto de Bryan como nunca haviam comprado antes e a <a href="http://videofruit.com/blog/2016-year-review/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">receita foi de $900.000 para $1,5 milhão</a> em menos de 12 meses:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-1024x575.png" alt="VideoFruit Yearly Booked Revenue" class="wp-image-90529" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-300x168.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-768x431.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-380x213.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue.png 1095w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Embora seja impossível saber quanto a série de documentário impactou diretamente a receita anual da Videofruit (somente Bryan sabe isso), poucos podem negar o poder influenciador de destacar os sucessos dos clientes.</p>



<p>Existe algo em dar aos potenciais clientes uma ideia de como sua vida poderia ser se eles fizerem uma compra; algo que leva a publicidade de um produto a um outro nível.</p>



<p>Filmar um documentário não é para qualquer um. E pode não ser para você ou para o seu negócio. Mas mais empreendedores estão optando por vídeos mais profissionais para estimular a venda de seus produtos. E por uma boa razão: isso funciona.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Tarefa:</strong>&nbsp;Pergunte aos seus atuais clientes como a vida deles mudou após ter comprado o seu produto e os apresente em um documentário destacando sua transformação.</p>




